      "options": {
        "content": "**Data path**\n\n`dpinger` (running on pfSense) -> Unix sockets at `/var/run/dpinger_*.sock` -> `/usr/local/bin/dpinger_textfile_30s.sh` (cron every 1m, runs twice for 30s cadence) -> `/var/tmp/node_exporter/dpinger.prom` -> `node_exporter` on `192.168.4.1:9100` -> Prometheus job `node{instance=\"pfsense\"}` -> Thanos.\n\n**IaC**\n- Scripts: `pfsense/scripts/dpinger_textfile{,_30s}.sh` (sync: `scripts/sync-pfsense-scripts.py`)\n- Cron: `pfsense/cron-jobs.yml` (sync: `scripts/sync-pfsense-cron-jobs.py`)\n- Prom target: `terraform/portainer/locals.tf` (`node` job, `instance=pfsense`)",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
